        </p>

        <h2>Use it with WPCNA</h2>
        <p>If you are thinking about starting a neighborhood association, this is a good first resource. Use it to get oriented, then reach out to WPCNA if you want help talking through the next step, finding out how other associations are organized, or getting connected to the wider council.</p>
